            "id": 6427536,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 集中市場加權指數上漲754.06點至37712.86點，漲幅2.04%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間21日12:13，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲754.06點（或2.04%），暫報37712.86點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+4.23%</li><li>近 1 月：+10.18%</li><li>近 3 月：+16.37%</li><li>近 6 月：+33.48%</li><li>今年以來：+27.6%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Flash模組概念領漲+7.72%。其中    品安(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8088:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8088\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8088-TW</a>)            上漲        9.98%            ;        廣穎(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4973:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4973\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4973-TW</a>)            上漲        9.95%            ;        威剛(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3260:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3260\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3260-TW</a>)            上漲        9.92%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>DRAM模組概念領漲+6.99%。其中    品安(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8088:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8088\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8088-TW</a>)            上漲        9.98%            ;        廣穎(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4973:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4973\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4973-TW</a>)            上漲        9.95%            ;        威剛(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3260:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3260\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3260-TW</a>)            上漲        9.92%    。</p></section></main>",
